Introduction

Dreamnote is a 6-member girl group under IMe Entertainment. The group currently consists of members: Boni, Youi, Lara, Miso, Sumin, and Eunjo.

Dreamnote was originally planned to debut with 9 members however Jinsol dropped out in June 2018. They debuted as 8 in November 2018 with the album "Dreamlike". On September 6, 2019, it was announced that Habin and Hanbyeol would be leaving the group due to personal reasons. Because of their departure, Dreamnote is now a 6-member group.
